# **Phase Overview**

| **Phase** | **Timeline** | **Goal** | **Status** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| MVP | Weeks 1 to 7 | Launch with core booking features. Get first 20 artists. | Build Now |
| Phase 2 | Month 3 to 6 | Grow to 100 artists. Add Instagram integration. | After Validation |
| Phase 3 | Month 6 to 12 | Expand beyond Lebanon. Add products catalogue. | After Revenue |
| Phase 4 | Year 2 and beyond | Scale to MENA. Add payments. Enterprise features. | Future |

| **Color** | **Meaning** |
