| Orange background | Phase 2 feature — built after first users |
| Purple background | Phase 3 feature — built after first revenue |
| Pink background | Phase 4 feature — long term vision |

# **1. Customer Features**

| **Feature** | **Phase** | **Description** | **Why This Phase** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Register and login | MVP | Email and password account creation with JWT auth | Core requirement for booking |
| Browse artist profiles | MVP | View artist name, bio, city, photos, and rating | Customers need to discover artists |
| Search and filter artists | MVP | Filter by service type, city, and price range | Essential for discovery |
| View artist portfolio | MVP | See artist's work photos before booking | Trust builder before booking |
| View services and prices | MVP | See all services an artist offers with prices | Needed to make booking decision |
| Check availability | MVP | See available time slots for a specific date | Core booking requirement |
| Create booking request | MVP | Request an appointment with chosen artist | Core platform function |
| Receive booking confirmation | MVP | Email notification when artist confirms | Customer needs to know status |
| View booking history | MVP | See past and upcoming appointments | Basic account feature |
| Cancel a booking | MVP | Cancel with platform cancellation policy | Needed for user control |
| Leave a review | MVP | Rate artist and leave comment after appointment | Builds platform trust |
| Receive booking reminders | MVP | Email reminder 24 hours before appointment | Reduces no-shows |
| PWA install prompt | MVP | Option to add B-Edge to home screen | Improves retention |
| Instagram booking link | MVP | Artist shares B-Edge profile link in Instagram bio | First Instagram integration |
| Arabic and English UI | MVP | Full bilingual interface | Lebanon market requirement |
| Social login | Phase 2 | Login with Google or Apple account | Reduces signup friction |
| Favourite artists | Phase 2 | Save preferred artists for quick rebooking | Improves retention |
| Rebook previous service | Phase 2 | One tap to rebook a past appointment | Convenience feature |
| Instagram Book Now button | Phase 2 | Book directly from artist Instagram profile | Major discovery channel |
| In-app chat with artist | Phase 2 | Message artist before or after booking | Replaces WhatsApp for service queries |
| Push notifications | Phase 2 | Browser push for booking updates | Better than email only |
| Referral system | Phase 2 | Share B-Edge and earn discounts | Growth mechanism |
| Browse by neighbourhood | Phase 2 | Find artists near specific Beirut areas | Hyper local discovery |
| Gift a booking | Phase 3 | Send a booking as a gift to someone | New revenue stream |
| Buy beauty products | Phase 3 | Purchase products sold by artists | New revenue stream |
| Loyalty points | Phase 3 | Earn points per booking redeemable for discounts | Retention program |
| Multi country support | Phase 3 | Use B-Edge in Jordan, Egypt, UAE | MENA expansion |
| Video consultation | Phase 4 | Video call with artist before booking | Premium feature |
| AI style recommendations | Phase 4 | AI suggests artists based on face shape and preferences | Differentiation |
| Online payments | Phase 4 | Pay for booking online via local gateway | Requires payment partner |
| Subscription packages | Phase 4 | Buy monthly bundles with favourite artist | Recurring revenue |

